race.description: Aussie Rocks Tasmanian Gold Cup F Division1
race.comment: APPENZELL (3) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including five wins. Recorded a 4.5 lengths win (25.62) in a OPEN last time at this track. Expected to be in the finish. SLICK FELIX (8) copped a check in the run last time but wound up strongly to hit the frame when third (26.16) in a OPEN at this track. Worth another try. FUEL ON FOUR (7) comes off a (25.66) win last time, scoring by 0.8 lengths in a OPEN over 461m at this track. Has two wins already from this draw. Can hit the frame with the right run. TIMES FLYING (1) has claims if she runs up to her best.
